"data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"DISTRESS_ORCHID_COLONY_FIRE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "(Frostwall) Ask Frostwall to use his ice powers to stop the fire."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append:12
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_ORCHID_COLONY_FIRE_DEATHBLOOM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Despite being a crystal, Frostwall is eager to help and quickly springs into action. He conjures a blizzard over the entire colony, which quickly subdues the fire in a matter of seconds, sparing every last Orchid left inside. \n"
"        \n"
"        The Orchids are beyond grateful. They shower you with gifts and vow to spread word of your good deeds to the Multiverse."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append:17
msgid ""
